        "text": "#Repression ([[Psychological repression]]), usually used by the [[superego]] and ego against instinctive impulses, but on occasion employed against the superego/conscience itself.  If the defence fails, then (in a return of the repressed) one may begin to feel guilty years later for actions lightly committed at the time."
